    "history-list-09": "VK Entertainment JSC is established in 2009, which was formerly as VK Media. Our major business are: Event & Show organization, Management,Production, Distribution.",
    "history-list-12": "In 2012, we organized the K-POP FESTIVAL in Hanoi, with the participation of 78 Korean Singers and Groups",
