    "history-list-18": "In October 2018, VK Entertainment was the organizer of Here We Go Kpop Tour Season 1, with VTV Cab, Korean Cultural Center, Yeosim Seoul.",
    "history-list-23": "History was made as VK Entertainment successfully hosted <D'festa'> – the grandest K-POP stars exhibition from Korea – marking its highly anticipated debut in Vietnam. Held at Times City Shopping Mall, Hanoi, from October 14th to November 30th, 2023, 'D'festa' offered an unforgettable artistic experience.",
    "history-list-25": "In 2025, VK Entertainment brought the copyright of the KBS Music Bank program to Vietnam. Create opportunities for V-Pop artists to show their talents, contribute to the development and enhancement of the value of Vietnamese music.",
