  "DK-title-1": "Welcome to the digital services of VK Entertainment Joint Stock Company ('VK Entertainment', 'We', 'Our Company'). These Terms of Service (‘Terms’) govern your access to and use of our products, services, applications, websites (including vkentertainment.net), content, features, and other technologies (hereinafter collectively referred to as the ‘Services’)",
