  "DK-title-22": "3. Profile Information: You agree that your profile information (profile picture, display name, etc.) may be publicly displayed on the Services, subject to your privacy settings.",
  "DK-title-23": "4. Account Termination: We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time without prior notice if you violate any of these Terms or if we believe that continued provision of Services to you would be harmful to us or third parties.",
  "DK-title-24": "1. You commit to using the Services lawfully, responsibly, and in compliance with all applicable laws of Vietnam, as well as our policies and guidelines.",
